      "text": "2. A/C filter removal"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "874_5.0_jpn_11580964_5.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Remove the left and right locks (A) and remove the lid (B). Pull out and remove the filter element (C)."
    },
    {
      "type": "attention",
      "items": [
        "Do not clean the filter element."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "3. Precautions for installation work"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Installation is the reverse of the removal procedure."
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        {
          "text": "When installing the A/C filter, install it with the arrow of the AIR FLOW mark pointing downward."
        },
        {
          "text": "When installing the A/C filter, install it with the arrow of the AIR FLOW mark pointing downward."
        },
        {
          "text": "Install the lid securely and make sure there are no air leaks."
        },
